In 2020 i made the first revision of my print in place 0.5in hex collar. and in the last few months i have decided to revisit this concept and improve it further.

So i made the banana collar!

This revision greatly improves the holding force of the collar while reducing the wear of the printed part in operation!

For more details and the files for printing and remixing here is the link.
